    "English": "Local mineral extract, typically found in large deposits or extracted from common minerals after inspection with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br><br>Typically found on planets with a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">tropical environment</span>.",
