    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">石蜡</span>常见于拥有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">热带环境</span>的星球上<br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>定位遍布于大型资源点中的此类资源",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">鑞</span>主要可見於<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">熱帶環境</span>的世界<br>常見於大型資源產地，可使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>找到"
